title: 304: Top-5 most explosive players in the NFL
itunes:title: 304: Top-5 most explosive players in the NFL
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks rank the NFL divisions by quarterback (2:00). The guys then chat the most improved offenses in the league (21:20), and wrap things up by counting down the top-5 most explosive players in the NFL right now (33:50).
